  "3257320": {
    "name": "Square Jump",
    "steam_appid": 3257320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you been looking for a simple game where you are a cube and want to jump on different things? Square Jump is perfect!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a square that must get as far as possible from the destination, or the finish line, without dying or falling into traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 2 types of enemies, the black square and the red square. The black square has no gravity and you can't kill it, but the red square has gravity and you can kill it if you jump on it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The buttons are colored according to the doors, and if you press them, the doors will open. Just like the boxes, if you put them in the colored areas according to the same color, you will be able to open other doors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a lot of levels, but also achievements waiting for you to complete them all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy!</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
